cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with crowd scene analysis and proposes a Multi-Stream Convolutional Neural Network for crowd counting.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes an end-to-end solution using deep learning techniques.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a neural network architecture and investigates the influence of different ground truth generation methods.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing images and generating density maps.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category as the paper mentions surveillance and security applications, but the main focus is on crowd counting using computer vision techniques.
